We only receive partial frames on the Lidar topic over GigE. Wireshark shows =
fragmentation.
Should we enable jumbo frames (MTU 9000) on the Orin NX interface, or keep 15=
00 and lower the packet rate?

---
Reply:
Start with MTU 1500 and verify switch port settings. If the network supports =
end-to-end jumbo frames, MTU 9000 can help for high-rate pointcloud streams; =
otherwise enable software packet reassembly in the driver.
